  <!-- =====================================================================
       Description
  ====================================================================== -->
  <spirit:description>
    PCIe 7.0 Controller IP: full TLP/DLL/PHY stack with AXI4 interface,
    DMA engine, MSI/MSI-X, AER, power management (L0s/L1/L2),
    completion timeout, and CDC synchronizers. Parameterized x1-x16,
    Gen1-Gen7. Includes formal (SymbiYosys), UVM testbench, lint waivers,
    SDC constraints, and UPF power intent.
  </spirit:description>

